![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9aaafadb-3fa3-4412-9781-61fd7e572f8f/21056.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SETH ROLLINS STRIPPED OF WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP; BATTLE ROYALE SET TO DETERMINE WHO WILL FACE CM PUNK FOR THE TITLE_**
    

Adam Pearce tries to make an announcement but he's interrupted by the Brons.

Once they hit the ring, Adam announced that Rollins has been stripped of the World Heavyweight Championship. He asks Bron Breakker for the title back.

Bron Breakker says what if he doesn't want to give it back? Heyman tries to convince Bron to give it back. Bron says maybe Pearce should say it with more respect.

Pearce asks respectfully.

Bron says maybe Adam Pearce should say please.

Adam Pearce says please.

Bron laughs and hands the belt to Paul Heyman who gives it to Adam Pearce.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d4b95946-db5c-491e-b784-76ea5e5d66f2/21057.jpg?format=original)

Paul Heyman says he gets it, he also watched WWE Unreal. They're the bad guys, they're the "heels".

But he doesn't understand why people are mad. The Vision was NEVER about Seth Rollins. Paul Heyman did not turn on Roman and Punk for Seth. He turned on them because Bron Breakker is the future and Bronson Reed is better than Roman Reigns.

How could Seth Rollins talk about the future when he's standing there with his bum shoulder. Unable to carry the burden.

Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed conspired to take Seth Rollins Main Event spot. Paul Heyman says this is not revisionist history, this is a RE-VISION of the future.

Welcome to Monday Night RAW.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/19b9c5c6-afcd-4c77-acc4-062ae25fbdb0/21062.jpg?format=original)

Finn Balor and JD McDonough are pissed with Dom for getting them into a tag title defense against AJ Styles and Dragon Lee this week.

Dom says he doesn't understand how they're mad when he defends his belts every week, and he's already beaten AJ Styles.

Balor and JD say Dom can handle his defense against Rusev on his own because they're getting ready for their match. They leave.

Roxanne wants Dom to relax. He's great. He's got this.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/76b886e8-44f0-4a58-89a3-f75dcde3b4b9/21069.jpg?format=original)

## **_AJ Styles and Dragon Lee are the new World Tag Team Champions!!!_**

*   ## **_AJ Styles and Dragon Lee def. Judgement Day in an EXCELLENT match!!_**
    

