The line-up for the World Heavyweight Championship #1 Contender Over the Top Battle Royale

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/68f42e8f-6e08-458f-b767-9ed5eb56e69b/21082.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_Intercontinental Championship: Dominik Mysterio def. Rusev_**
    

Dom tries to leave with his championships but Penta appears and stops him. Rusev attacks Penta and Dom steals the ringside hammer.

Rusev catches Dom with the hammer, the ref catches Rusev with the hammer, Dom low blows and hits a frog splash for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fa744e34-c898-48c5-9000-c582dc415be9/21091.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE Women's Intercontinental Championship: Maxxine Dupri def. Becky Lynch by DQ_**
    

Becky Lynch has enough of Maxxine's luck, so she smacks her with the title and beats her down after the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e441cd10-3650-45e7-b495-b5bc0b0f8cdd/21092.jpg?format=original)

Asuka is done with Iyo and Rhea. She broke Iyo's spirit and she ruined Rhea's return to Australia at Crown Jewel.

Asuka is happy that Kairi finally showed her ruthless side last week when they attacked Rhea and Iyo.

Now the Kabuki Warriors want a new challenge. They want gold and they're putting the entire Women Tag Team Division on hold

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5212f573-831e-47aa-86be-d0c405dba16d/21097.jpg?format=original)

Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed have been REMOVED from the World Heavyweight Championship Battle Royale

Heyman turned around and runs into Becky Lynch. Heyman tries to convince Becky Lynch that he only turned on Seth Rollins because he needed to survive. Heyman says Becky still has a place in the Vision.

Becky grabs him by the neck and says Rollins always knew Heyman would turn, he even wondered why it took so long.

When Rollins returns, he's not going to hurt Heyman. He's going to make Heyman watch him take down whatever nepo baby he's decided to attach himself to at that time.

