![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cee56515-cb29-4686-a1d6-b1620c36f806/21105.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_Stephanie Vaquer def. Roxanne Perez_**
    

Raquel and Roxanne jumped Stephanie after the match but Nikki Bella runs out to even the odds!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d9593053-1eca-4d9e-ae2c-8c37f222a01d/21107.jpg?format=original)

The screen went black and the camera focused on Roxanne Perez and Raquel Rodriguez after the post match angle on RAW.

When the camera finally cut back to Nikki Bella and Stephanie Vaquer, Nikki was desperately trying to keep her top back together.

