*   ## **_Jey Uso wins the World Heavyweight Championship #1 Contenders Battle Royale by throwing his own brother over and finally Dirty Dom._**
    

Jey Uso will face CM Punk for the World Heavyweight Championship on November 1st at Saturday Nights Main Event